    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014well-loved and runs like a dream! You might find a few tiny signs of use here and there, but it still looks fantastic and handles the road beautifully. It\u2019s super reliable and totally ready for its next adventure with you. Feel free to reach out if you want to come see it or take it for a spin!",
