    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a remarkably well-maintained vehicle that perfectly captures the balance between a daily driver and a pride-of-ownership machine. The exterior maintains a brilliant shine and deep color, though a close inspection will reveal the minor, expected stone chips and light surface scratches that come with careful road use. Step inside to a smoke-free cabin where the premium upholstery remains firm and supportive; the leather shows only light natural creasing on the driver's side bolster, and the carpets have been protected by floor mats since day one. Every feature, from the intuitive touchscreen navigation to the heated seats and dual-zone climate control, operates exactly as it should. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health, benefiting from a documented history of on-time oil changes and fluid flushes. The engine runs quietly, the transmission shifts are crisp and predictable, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. With plenty of tread remaining on the tires, this vehicle is truly turn-key and ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 34500.0,
