    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me\u2014definitely a 'get in and go' kind of ride! It\u2019s been well-loved and looked after, so while it isn't fresh off the lot, it still looks great and drives even better. I\u2019d love for someone to enjoy it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
