      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust BMW E46 M3, featuring the high-strung S54 inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This example has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS bulletproofing kit, ensuring the chassis and valvetrain can handle the 8,000 RPM redline. The ZF 6-speed manual gearbox offers precise gate engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential for optimal torque vectoring. Suspension geometry remains true with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, providing the tactile feedback and turn-in precision this platform is known for. While the exterior shows minor road-going character, the drivetrain remains in peak operational harmony.",
